data.description: Wake up to sprawling views of the Chesapeake Bay with sandy beaches and all that comes with Bay living lifestyle all months of the year. This 2 bedroom and 2 full bathroom top floor condo, has been meticulously cared for, with the current owner having recently given the condo a fresh paint job, upgraded the appliances and installed new flooring throughout. The two large skylights in the living room and upgraded kitchen area provide great light all throughout the day and your large balcony overlooking the Bay is just outside your living room sliding door. Enjoy your private ensuite with a walk-in shower and large rear facing balcony just off your bedroom to let the fresh bay air wake you up and watch the sunsets every day, and enjoy your inviting fireplace in the living room during the colder months on the Bay. Condo fees cover master insurance policy on the exterior of the building, trash pick-up, all ground maintenance, and private assigned parking.
